rsebut, mengajak warga untuk terus melestarikan budaya ini.\n\n“Festival ini menjadi bukti kecintaan kita terhadap budaya lokal. Semua elemen masyarakat berpartisipasi, dan tradisi seperti ini harus terus dijaga dan diwariskan,” ujar Tri.\n\n#kotabekasi \n#kotapatriot","post_time":1745838863,"owner":"68258708641","username":"bks.jabar.jabodetabek","comment_count":0,"like_count":105,"cdn_image":"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/pemkotbekasi/photo_gallery/picture/68258708641/DI_PXvaTPyg.jpg"},{"id":"DI_IHW1SWye","image":"https://scontent-fra3-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/491895626_18400140043110987_2571639733914886797_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p720x720_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6IkNBUk9VU0VMX0lURU0uaW1hZ2VfdXJsZ2VuLjEwODB4MTM1MC5zZHIuZjc1NzYxLmRlZmF1bHRfaW1hZ2UifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-fra3-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=103&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2QFeQF2DFusNZznEe0UYd7G0RYHYagptHQpv5Gf_z2v4jQSWiWFi1hidvlcOwSY5zKI&_nc_ohc=ieYT_xPh_jwQ7kNvwFtrQfK&_nc_gid=-DrKNG5AzTbOvpRoevdAbQ&edm=APoiHPcBAAAA&ccb=7-5&ig_cache_key=MzYyMDY0ODMwNTcxNTU0MzM0OA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&oh=00_AfPi1YpWJfaVDW0k2yWJKcTIP7uEDTjbqBazLQ7K8n82kg&oe=68680507&_nc_sid=22de04","caption":"Giat K3 Aparatur se-Kecamatan Mustikajaya di Stadion Mini H. Natrom Nursyamsu","post_time":1745834935,"owner":"68258708641","username":"bks.jabar.jabodetabek","comment_count":0,"like_count":46,"cdn_image":"//cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/pemkotbekasi/photo_gallery/picture/68258708641/DI_IHW1SWye.jpg"},{"id":"DI_EviNS8Q8","image":"https://scontent-fra5-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/492152972_18222232972292719_4991619897798497488_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_cat=109&ig_cache_key=MzYyMDYzMzQ4NDE2MDkxMDM5Ng%3D%3D.3-ccb1-7&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=58cdad&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjU0MHg5NjAuc2RyIn0%3D&_nc_ohc=F6Iv3U3qGFUQ7kNvwF-FMkF&_nc_oc=AdlSbh--HmbWkfUfwTanXACNiZIW6bv2weWQONG2LuGxDLh2AP7a_KGOaEcfrP8wme4&_nc_ad=z-m&_nc_cid=0&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_gid=-DrKNG5AzTbOvpRoevdAbQ&oh=00_AfOf6tm1Z_qAKQco3yXBu5oQdy83cNkMea3BmgxnvMzaoA&oe=686801D4"